title: War of the Roses: I'd Say There's a 99% Chance He's Cheating
description: Kara called the show today for War of the Roses! She's concerned about her Boyfriend, Pete, who've been dating for over a year now. One major red flag is he's been deleting his tags off of posts she's posting. There's more but we trapped Pete to reveal the truth!
